Marc Cavell (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marc_Cavell_(actor) 0 Marc Edward Cavell (June 28, 1939 – February 29, 2004) was an American actor.He performed in sixteen films from 1949 to 1978. Television guest-credits include Peter Gunn, Alfred Hitchcock Presents, and The Twilight Zone.
